{"tid":1221482,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全球黑衫口罩「計埋我行動」(海外朋友係時候發功)","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T22:56:08.000Z","uid":260942,"like":226,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0b70f0ee2c7ab2b8f07891060d38410c2ddeadfd","tid":1221482,"uid":260942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的，細嘅人在海外想撐香港，但已經唔想再9行集會叫口號，完全R不到癢處。忽發奇想，唔知大家有無聽過見過外國No Pants Subway Ride，啲人集埋一齊唔著褲若無其事咁去搭地鐵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/images.hamlethub.com/hhresized/original/3327/201501/00013261_H35602645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages.hamlethub.com%2Fhhresized%2Foriginal%2F3327%2F201501%2F00013261_H35602645.jpg&h=a9782857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我提議全世界香港人，甚至係撐香港人嘅外國朋友，吹雞喺星期日約埋一齊全部戴頭盔眼罩口罩著黑衫去坐地鐵/公共交通。<br />\n<br />\n做法可以係，約埋十幾個一團，從四方百面搭地鐵去遊行或集會地點，集會完再散水去各大景點地標打卡。整返個hashtag，就算各自分散做都得，又無language barrier，可以邀請外國朋友都參加。<br />\n<br />\n件事最重要係gimmick，要令全世界傳媒都報之餘，唔理時事嘅外國人都有興趣睇。因為呢個世上係超多人係唔睇新聞，世界發生咩事都唔知，只係活喺自己嘅bubble，只睇IG Facebook花邊新聞trending YouTube。<br />\n<br />\n叫&quot;計埋我行動&quot; Hong Kong Count Me In，數遊行人數時請計埋海外嘅我，多一個已經好多。和理非就是民意牌，令到中間游份子出黎。個hashtag叫#hkcountmein，一人成行，多人更佳！<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點？係做就快啲發散開去，除左要俾遊行搞手知，等佢哋可以幫手呼籲，仲要俾全世界去到山卡啦嘅香港人，就算佢地當地無集會，都可以做到啲嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da393a84ded2425c6fce4ee81b3ed110c5758af","tid":1221482,"uid":260942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ba54b06e3c7bb3610a540719a055a76cdc130f7","tid":1221482,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7260d8f50074e351e2d98120a40c83c22ddbe0d6","tid":1221482,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"fd13371dff5a9c7783b8ca4aa8a06110f2453df6","tid":1221482,"uid":139199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a569f0777c32cc7a8c9e2cb52120ffad05579391","tid":1221482,"uid":53983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9be76fdd2b5b0f4c849a19c5857900660112fd04","tid":1221482,"uid":114497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e01449b8b9225e0b397a8f552854b1171eeacf3c","tid":1221482,"uid":260942,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"自推！ <br />\n<br />\n一人成行，多人更佳！著黑衫+口罩坐公共交通工具影相打卡，戴埋頭盔、眼罩更perfect池，去埋全球各地嘅地標打卡當然仲正啦！upload上facebook、instagram、twitter加埋hashtag #hkcountmein，大家集氣！希望世界各地嘅人都知逃犯條例嘅禍害，黑警幾咁痴線！咁簡單，唔係唔join嘛？<br />\n#hkcountmein #香港計埋我"},{"pid":"e6cfccb01779d2643001a59c3d943dd170283abf","tid":1221482,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d57360cd29068dc0df4ed99fcb1582c9714ca021","tid":1221482,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n諗得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7115d0bfd44d6c60c24a932eff0b7273f574e675","tid":1221482,"uid":152061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93a556e48a5a2e4e3f3b545d00d81e62d85b9404","tid":1221482,"uid":18639,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"唔係想打擊你 但真心覺得無乜用<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要 兄弟爬山 各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac43516881fb29b8b446749619c46aef173bbb0","tid":1221482,"uid":260942,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"93a556e48a5a2e4e3f3b545d00d81e62d85b9404","tid":1221482,"uid":18639,"like":4,"dislike":12,